sparql_query.0: SELECT ?mammal ?mammalLabel WHERE { ?mammal wdt:P31 wd:Q7377 . SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language 'en' . } }
sparql_query.1: SELECT ?bird ?birdLabel WHERE { ?bird wdt:P31 wd:Q5113 . SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language 'en' . } }
sparql_query.4: SELECT ?taxonName WHERE { wd:Q7377 wdt:P225 ?taxonName. SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language 'en' . } }
sparql_query.5: SELECT ?subclass ?subclassLabel WHERE { ?subclass wdt:P279 wd:Q7380. SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language '[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en'. }}
sparql_query.6: SELECT ?animal ?animalLabel ?rank ?rankLabel WHERE { ?animal wdt:P31 wd:Q729 . ?animal wdt:P105 ?rank . SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language 'en' . } }
sparql_query.7: SELECT ?taxon ?taxonLabel ?population WHERE { ?taxon wdt:P31 wd:Q16521. ?taxon wdt:P1082 ?population. SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language '[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en'. }} ORDER BY DESC(?population) LIMIT 1
